     1	//! Recursive-descent parser for Markdown plans.
     2	//!
     3	//! Responsibilities:
     4	//! - Extract the rhei title and pre-Tasks content sections.
     5	//! - Parse YAML frontmatter, including the plan-level `structure` block
     6	//!   (`maxLevels`, `nodeKinds`).
     7	//! - Build the recursive task tree from H3..=H6 node headings, using the
     8	//!   configured `nodeKinds` to accept the leading keyword.
     9	//! - Attach child nodes to parents based on id-segment extension and heading
    10	//!   depth.
