     6	#[test]
     7	fn malformed_structure_near_misses_fall_back_to_text_tokens() {
     8	    // `### task 1: Wrong Case` is still matched because kind matching is
     9	    // case-insensitive at semantic layers; here the lexer emits a NodeHeader
    10	    // with the authored casing and the parser is the one that applies the
    11	    // case-insensitive kind lookup. `#### Task 1: Missing Decimal Component`
    12	    // is a valid node heading lexically; the parser rejects it because a
